Name: anal gland neoplasm
Definition: A chondrosarcoma that is located_in exclusively soft tissue.

Name: anus leiomyoma
Definition: A gastrointestinal system benign neoplasm that derives_from smooth muscle cells and that is located_in the anus.

Name: anal neuroendocrine tumor
Definition: A fallopian tube carcinoma that derives_from squamous epithelial cells.
